{"tid":286284,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳瀅接受「地盤佬」追求","createTime":"2017-06-16T13:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T14:05:35.000Z","uid":31314,"like":7,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74c26912d3079fe38372cc31a8556a36b96f0721","tid":286284,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"陳瀅、傅嘉莉（Kelly）與劉江等，前晚出席「築．動．愛」記者會。陳瀅透露拍攝節目時撞正黑雨，地盤充斥泥濘，恍如山泥傾瀉般，令她一步一驚心。與劉江飾演兩父女的她大讚對方專業，不但自己的對白一字不漏，連她的部分也全背了，劉老師更在合照時笑說：「才剛拍完又掛住我喇！」笑爆全場！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">問到會否接受「地盤佬」的追求？陳瀅坦言不介意，皆因自己也愛吃「地盤佬飯」，例如豆腐火腩飯，故雙方在口味上有共通點。</span><br />\n<br />\n另外，經常與富豪傳緋聞的Kelly，亦不抗拒與建造業人士拍拖，她說：「我也有個男生朋友做科文，薪水很好又不危險，其實從事建造業比做藝人的收入更穩定，如果靚仔就更好啦！」<br />\n<br />\n地盤猛鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a6fddef5499d3c960ced15684776643710a2a9","tid":286284,"uid":109050,"like":127,"dislike":0,"score":127,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:07:27.000Z","msg":"扮撚曬野"},{"pid":"7ee4b7d2deda789a7729d5bd14ff38e958e8d0dd","tid":286284,"uid":43861,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扮撚曬野</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2964f054a2376b443868e3d64d86f0d0416221a4","tid":286284,"uid":1289,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f5adf16b9c9e928a628057fc1dbb0302d0d3a86b","tid":286284,"uid":34419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"好撚假"},{"pid":"bd2816a3f14413c770f58bee9421a9287a9513e5","tid":286284,"uid":89999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:11:25.000Z","msg":"哇好pure 呀"},{"pid":"51e509fe2b82ac608b4757d88ef40dce6d3dbf3e","tid":286284,"uid":31314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T13:12:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地工程界又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n猛鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" cla